      "id": "sybil_7_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? I\u2019m parting with this absolute beauty, and let me tell you, it is in pristine, mint condition! It\u2019s been pampered since day one\u2014garage-kept, smoke-free, and meticulously cared for. It drives like a dream and honestly looks brand new. You won\u2019t find another one this clean! Come take a look, you're going to fall in love!",
      "price": 44900.0,
