    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54B32 3.2L inline-six. This specimen is mechanically flawless, boasting a factory Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock. The high-revving powerplant maintains exceptional compression, with the double VANOS system and rod bearings proactively addressed to ensure peak valvetrain synchronization and bottom-end longevity. The chassis integrity is absolute, featuring a reinforced rear subframe to mitigate common floor pan fatigue. Finished in concours-level Carbon Black Metallic, the exterior retains its factory depth with original VIN tags on all panels. The suspension remains taut with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, providing the precise lateral dynamics this platform is renowned for. A meticulously documented service history accompanies this collector-quality vehicle.",
      "price": 48500.0,
